+```text
+(∂t + ν|k|^2) u_{s_k}(k)
+  = ∑_{τ : k+p+q=0} C_τ overline{u_{s_p}(p)} overline{u_{s_q}(q)}.
+```
+
+Write
+
+```text
+u_{s_j}(j) = a_j e^{i φ_j},
+C_τ = |C_τ| e^{-i ψ_τ}.
+```
+
+Then the exact triad phase variable is
+
+```text
+Φ_τ := φ_k + φ_p + φ_q + ψ_τ
+     = arg(C_τ u_{s_k}(k) u_{s_p}(p) u_{s_q}(q)).
+```
+
+[CHECKED] The corresponding exact contribution to the mode-energy equation of leg
+`k` is
+
+```text
+T_{τ→k} = 2 |C_τ| a_k a_p a_q cos(Φ_τ).
+```
+
